<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 06:15:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日经新闻称，中国比亚迪计划在墨西哥新建电动汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-plans-new-electric-vehicle-plant-mexico-says-nikkei-2024-02-13/</link><description>《日经新闻》周三援引该公司墨西哥负责人的话说，中国比亚迪有限公司将在墨西哥建立一家新的电动汽车（EV）工厂，该电动汽车制造商的目标是建立一个对美国的出口中心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 18:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-plans-new-electric-vehicle-plant-mexico-says-nikkei-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：印度IT部担心在智能手机出口竞赛中输给中国和越南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/india-it-ministry-fears-losing-out-china-vietnam-smartphone-exports-race-2024-02-13/</link><description>印度信息技术部副部长​​在路透社看到的政府文件中表示，印度在寻求成为主要智能手机出口中心时面临着输给中国和越南的风险，必须“迅速采取行动”以较低关税吸引全球企业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/india-it-ministry-fears-losing-out-china-vietnam-smartphone-exports-race-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚贸易部长要求中国解除壁垒，质疑王判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-trade-minister-ask-china-lift-barriers-query-wang-sentence-2024-02-13/</link><description>澳大利亚贸易部长周二表示，他将于本月在阿布扎比举行的世界贸易组织会议上与中国贸易部长会面，并推动取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒、龙虾和肉类的进口限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:20:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-trade-minister-ask-china-lift-barriers-query-wang-sentence-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>印度在MSCI关键指数中缩小与中国的差距，权重再创新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-weightage-climbs-record-high-msci-global-standard-index-2024-02-13/</link><description>在最新修订后，印度在摩根士丹利资本国际全球标准指数（该指数为投资者追踪新兴市场股票）中缩小了与中国的差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 02:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-weightage-climbs-record-high-msci-global-standard-index-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀数据公布后，股市下跌，美元和收益率上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-13/</link><description>数据显示1月份美国通胀放缓幅度低于预期，全球股市指数下跌，10年期美国国债收益率触及2-1/2个月高点，美元兑日元触及三个月高位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 02:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>通胀数据公布后美元升至三个月高位并突破150日元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-nears-150-yen-ahead-us-inflation-test-bitcoin-buoyant-2024-02-13/</link><description>数据显示美国1月份通胀升幅超出预期，强化了美联储将在3月份维持利率稳定的预期，周二美元升至三个月高位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 01:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-nears-150-yen-ahead-us-inflation-test-bitcoin-buoyant-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：日元兑美元接近 150 十字路口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 21:57:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>沃伦·巴菲特 Squishmallows 的制造商 Build-A-Bear 在法庭上对峙</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/build-a-bear-maker-warren-buffetts-squishmallows-face-off-court-2024-02-12/</link><description>沃伦·巴菲特正在挑战“Build-A-Bear”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 20:59:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/build-a-bear-maker-warren-buffetts-squishmallows-face-off-court-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员呼吁对中国药明康德生物技术公司实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-lawmakers-call-sanctions-chinas-wuxi-apptec-biotech-firm-2024-02-12/</link><description>两党议员周一告诉拜登政府高级官员，美国应审查中国生物技术公司药明康德及其附属公司药明生物的制裁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 19:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-lawmakers-call-sanctions-chinas-wuxi-apptec-biotech-firm-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>民主党参议员对拜登竞选加入 TikTok 的决定表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-senator-raises-concerns-about-biden-campaign-decision-join-tiktok-2024-02-12/</link><description>参议院情报委员会主席周一表示，他对乔·拜登总统竞选团队加入短视频应用 TikTok 的决定感到担忧，而白宫表示，政府对国家安全的担忧没有任何改变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 19:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-senator-raises-concerns-about-biden-campaign-decision-join-tiktok-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>比特币两年多来首次触及 5 万美元水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bitcoin-hits-highest-more-than-two-years-2024-02-12/</link><description>比特币两年多来首次触及 50,000 美元的水平，全球最大的加密货币受到今年晚些时候降息的预期以及上个月美国监管机构批准旨在跟踪其价格的交易所交易基金的提振。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 15:40:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bitcoin-hits-highest-more-than-two-years-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：5,000 个乐观的理由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-12/</link><description>阿曼达·库珀 (Amanda Cooper) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 13:16:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>马克龙任命前能源署署长为未来亚欧走廊特使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/macron-names-former-engie-chief-envoy-future-asia-eu-corridor-2024-02-12/</link><description>法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命天然气公司前负责人恩吉为连接中东和南亚的跨国铁路和港口项目的特使，该项目被认为是中国“一带一路”倡议的替代方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 09:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/macron-names-former-engie-chief-envoy-future-asia-eu-corridor-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>股市稳定，美元上涨；投资者为CPI做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-pix-2024-02-12/</link><description>周一全球股指几乎没有变化，而美元在周二美国消费者价格指数报告之前小幅走高，该报告可能为美联储何时可能开始降息提供线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 09:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-pix-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>在通胀数据公布之前，美元在盘整模式中上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-us-inflation-data-tops-this-weeks-bill-2024-02-12/</link><description>美元兑主要货币周一小幅上涨，因投资者等待本周美国通胀和零售销售数据，以寻找美联储何时可能开始普遍预期的降息的线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 09:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-us-inflation-data-tops-this-weeks-bill-2024-02-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>